data.title: Population, Male (% Of Total)
data.meta_description: Population, male (% of total population) in Seychelles was reported at 52.55 % in 2023, according to the World Bank collection of development indicators, compiled from officially recognized sources. Seychelles - Population, male (% of total) - actual values, historical data, forecasts and projections were sourced from the World Bank on August of 2024.
